org.overture.ast.assistant

Interface IAstAssistant

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AUnionTypeAssistant, PAccessSpecifierAssistant, PDefinitionAssistant, PPatternAssistant, PTypeAssistant, SNumericBasicTypeAssistant

    public interface IAstAssistant
    IAstAssistant is an empty interface that is used to identify assistants in Overture.

    Assistants are defined as methods that: - are used in visitor cases as part of an Overture analysis - are used in 2 or more classes - take INode objects as input
    Author:
    ldc
